        <a class="px-2 py-1 md:px-3 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 border dark:border-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-700 transition-colors" href="/agendar">ğŸ“… <span class="hidden sm:inline">Agendar</span></a>
